uss.com.hk/images/smilies/default2/smile_47.gif"&gt;收租王都67....... 其它小業主情何以墈.....&lt;br&gt;&lt;br/&gt;收租王」永倫集團近期加速出售物業套現，據市場消息指，其近10年收購重建的銅鑼灣景隆街商廈地盤，近日以約7.5億元沽出，相較4年前透過舊樓強拍統一業權的購入價低一半。據悉，業主須負責完成重建物業，意味連同建築成本，恐怕須蝕讓超過10億元。&lt;br/&gt;該地盤屬於景隆街20至28號，前身為舊樓新安大廈，最初由新世界(00017)或相關人士所收購至8成業，在2018年轉售予永倫集團，及後永倫申請強拍並且在2021年年初成功以14.5億元統一業權。&lt;br/&gt;據市場消息指，該項目最新以7.5億元獲洽購，以項目獲重建樓面約8.1萬平方呎計算，每呎樓面地價約9,215元，相較2021年的強拍作價14.5億元低出48%。據了解，業主需要會一併負責興建項目，待完成後交予新買家，即除了地價外，買家在建築成本上亦有所虧蝕，總金額恐達逾十億元。&lt;br/&gt;&lt;br/&gt;據資料顯示，該地盤佔地近5,400平方呎，曾經批建1幢26層高商業大廈，另設一層地庫。&lt;br/&gt;永倫集團近期頻頻賣樓套現，其中最大銀碼包括早前以約2.3億元沽出中環甲級商廈「皇九」頂樓單位，7年慘蝕近6成；而永倫旗下茂盛控股(00022)今年初則以7.7億出售青衣永倫800酒店予機管局。至於目前永倫放售物業，還包括去年初放售灣仔商廈「永倫立方」市值約22億元，以及意向價7億元的長沙灣永倫大廈。&lt;br/&gt;&lt;br/&gt;&lt;a class="bburl" href="https://ps.hket.com/article/3974302/%E3%80%8C%E6%94%B6%E7%A7%9F%E7%8E%8B%E3%80%8D%E6%B0%B8%E5%80%AB%E5%82%B37.5%E5%84%84%E8%B3%A3%E9%8A%85%E9%91%BC%E7%81%A3%E6%99%AF%E9%9A%86%E8%A1%97%E5%95%86%E5%BB%88%E5%9C%B0%E7%9B%A4%20%20%E5%9C%B0%E5%83%B9%E9%80%A3%E5%BB%BA%E7%AF%89%E8%B2%BB%E6%81%90%E8%9D%95%E9%80%BE%E5%8D%81%E5%84%84?mtc=60037" target="_blank" uhash="91961774d49100cc263a9658af792abc"&gt;「收租王」永倫傳7.5億賣銅鑼灣景隆街商廈地盤 地價連建築費恐蝕逾十億&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/br&gt;&lt;/img&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br/&gt;&lt;br/&gt;&lt;br/&gt; &lt;!-- google_ad_section_end --&gt;&lt;/div&gt;</content><link href="https://www.discuss.com.hk/viewthread.php?tid=31973532&amp;extra=page%3D1%26amp%3Bfilter%3D0%26amp%3Borderby%3Ddateline%26amp%3Bascdesc%3DDESC&amp;tr_h=1032976614686851a2115911_51995665"/><published>2025-07-04T17:34:59+08:00</published></entry><entry><id>fe1529ad8e30f7c00b8fe09e934ca8eb</id><title>7師父 PK 湯博士 半年回顧</title><updated>2025-07-04T20:25:43+08:00</updated><author><name>mawingtai</name></author><content type="html">&lt;p&gt;Published on: 2025-07-04T20:25:43+0800&lt;/p&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;div class="postmessage-content t_msgfont" id="postmessage_573104571"&gt;&lt;!-- google_ad_section_start --&gt;&lt;span id="postorig_573104571"&gt;&lt;div class="embed-responsive embed-responsive-16by9"&gt;&lt;iframe allowfullscreen="" class="embed-responsive-item" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/aXL7cKLtD9M?wmode=transparent" wmode="Opaque"&gt;&lt;/iframe&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;a class="bburl" href="https://youtu.be/aXL7cKLtD9M?si=QHf5oIvbBGlnaDZ4" target="_blank"&gt;https://youtu.be/aXL7cKLtD9M?si=QHf5oIvbBGlnaDZ4&lt;/a&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;br/&gt;不知不覺過咗半年。&lt;br/&gt;湯sir 一邊繼續唱好繼續放貨。&lt;br/&gt;另一邊CCL已連升三週。&lt;br/&gt;倒底未來半年，係湯師父講既重拾樓巿gogogo，定係7師父咁講跌三多成？&lt;a class="postmorevideochannel" href="videochannel.php" title="進入香討影片區"&gt;進入香討影片區&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/br&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br/&gt;&lt;br/&gt;&lt;br/&gt; &lt;!-- google_ad_section_end --&gt;&lt;/div&gt;</content><link href="https://www.discuss.com.hk/viewthread.php?tid=31973614&amp;extra=page%3D1%26amp%3Bfilter%3D0%26amp%3Borderby%3Ddateline%26amp%3Bascdesc%3DDESC&amp;tr_h=1032976614686851a2115911_51995665"/><published>2025-07-04T20:25:43+08:00</published></entry><entry><id>adbbef2acdaff1d6aff504a073b66423</id><title>地產霸權再抬頭，施特首指點江山</title><updated>2025-07-04T21:49:02+08:00</updated><author><name>hkduck123</name></author><content type="html">&lt;p&gt;Published on: 2025-07-04T21:49:02+0800&lt;/p&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;div class="postmessage-content t_msgfont" id="postmessage_573105590"&gt;&lt;!-- google_ad_section_start --&gt;&lt;span id="postorig_573105590"&gt;&lt;div class="embed-responsive embed-responsive-16by9"&gt;&lt;iframe allowfullscreen="" class="embed-responsive-item" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/QQyQ9LxrDj0?wmode=transparent" wmode="Opaque"&gt;&lt;/iframe&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;a class="bburl" href="https://youtu.be/QQyQ9LxrDj0?si=5Yby2wneBnDtLm_o" target="_blank"&gt;https://youtu.be/QQyQ9LxrDj0?si=5Yby2wneBnDtLm_o&lt;/a&gt;&lt;a class="postmorevideochannel" href="videochannel.php" title="進入香討影片區"&gt;進入香討影片區&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br/&gt;&lt;br/&gt;&lt;br/&gt; &lt;!-- google_ad_section_end --&gt;&lt;/div&gt;</content><link href="https://www.discuss.com.hk/viewthread.php?tid=31973716&amp;extra=page%3D1%26amp%3Bfilter%3D0%26amp%3Borderby%3Ddateline%26amp%3Bascdesc%3DDESC&amp;tr_h=1032976614686851a2115911_51995665"/><published>2025-07-04T21:49:02+08:00</published></entry><entry><id>5a49dc344b4d37a8ca2ccdb2b257dd89</id><title>北京蘭州北京11天, 好長氣的遊記</title><updated>2025-07-03T09:18:46+08:00</updated><author><name>kc60wong</name></author><content type="html">&lt;p&gt;Published on: 2025-07-03T09:18:46+0800&lt;/p&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;div class="postmessage-content t_msgfont" id="postmessage_573084505"&gt;&lt;!-- google_ad_section_start --&gt;&lt;span id="postorig_573084505"&gt;第1天,6月11星期三&lt;br&gt;6月11出發,2人行,乘11.20西九高鐵,一等坐,人仔1997/人, 19.30到北京西站。&lt;br/&gt;近年好少出門,一年只上過幾次深圳。第一次坐高鐵,很興奮。&lt;br/&gt;當日早上10.00去站內添好運食D野,亦已在車上點了外賣。&lt;br/&gt;10.30食完,站內行下睇下, 11.00入閘安檢過關,11.10上車。&lt;br/&gt;原來車門會在開車前5min關閉。準時開車。&lt;br/&gt;個踏腳板安裝在前面坐位,於是後面位仁姐細細力伸一下腳,你就小震一下。&lt;br/&gt;在深圳北送上了KFC葡撻,廣州南送上了水蛋排骨飯, D野都OK好食。&lt;br/&gt;車上服務員送上免費飲品,小吃,似坐飛機。&lt;br/&gt;車上用alipay買了杯咖啡,poor。可能訊號弱,想網上定野比錢,好多失敗&lt;br/&gt;想定故宮門票,原來要好多日預定,最後在trip.com&lt;br/&gt;定了6月19,有領隊,有填鴨餐的票,約250/人。&lt;br/&gt;又定了13日恭王府門票, 20元/人。&lt;br/&gt;7.30準時到北京西。&lt;/br&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br/&gt;&lt;br/&gt;&lt;br/&gt; &lt;!-- google_ad_section_end --&gt;&lt;/div&gt;</content><link href="https://www.discuss.com.hk/viewthread.php?tid=31972442&amp;utm_source=festival_fid&amp;utm_medium=110&amp;utm_campaign=1076&amp;extra=page%3D1%26amp%3Bfilter%3D0%26amp%3Borderby%3Ddateline%26amp%3Bascdesc%3DDESC"/><published>2025-07-03T09:18:46+08:00</published></entry><entry><id>375893a4e3ce58e60012de67fe7e5a6e</id><title>到此一遊系列 - 馬巒山防詐騙玩水R荔枝一日遊</title><updated>2025-06-30T14:50:33+08:00</updated><author><name>kingkong_hk</name></author><content type="html">&lt;p&gt;Published on: 2025-06-30T14:50:33+0800&lt;/p&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;div class="postmessage-content t_msgfont" id="postmessage_573050416"&gt;&lt;!-- google_ad_section_start --&gt;&lt;span id="postorig_573050416"&gt;趁呢幾日落過雨要安排玩水路線, 馬巒山郊野公園位於龍崗區坪山, 要預較多交通時間&lt;br&gt;&lt;br/&gt;&lt;br/&gt;&lt;br/&gt;&lt;br/&gt;由蓮塘口岸打車來碧嶺入口(西北門)大約45分鐘, 高鐵西九龍去高鐵坪山站55分鐘仲可以順手玩埋雲巴, 再轉駁公車過來大約30分鐘&lt;br/&gt;&lt;span class="post-img-container" data-pid="573050416" original-img="http://album.king-kong.org/china/MaluanHill/IMG_20250629_111849.jpg" style='\"display:block\"'&gt;&lt;img border="0" data-src="https://album.king-kong.org/china/MaluanHill/IMG_20250629_111849.jpg" src="https://cdn.discuss.com.hk/t/5ccc0b/f/800x0/http://album.king-kong.org/china/MaluanHill/IMG_20250629_111849.jpg"/&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br/&gt;&lt;br/&gt;唔熟地形睇呢個地圖都幾R頭, 今次係來玩碧嶺瀑布群步道&lt;br/&gt;&lt;span class="post-img-container" data-pid="573050416" original-img="http://album.king-kong.org/china/MaluanHill/IMG_20250629_112756.jpg" style='\"display:block\"'&gt;&lt;img border="0" data-src="https://album.king-kong.org/china/MaluanHill/IMG_20250629_112756.jpg" src="https://cdn.discuss.com.hk/t/bd6289/f/800x0/http://album.king-kong.org/china/MaluanHill/IMG_20250629_112756.jpg"/&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br/&gt;&lt;br/&gt;反詐騙主題公園乜都冇算唔算詐騙&lt;br/&gt;&lt;span class="post-img-container" data-pid="573050416" original-img="http://album.king-kong.org/china/MaluanHill/IMG_20250629_112927.jpg" style='\"display:block\"'&gt;&lt;img border="0" data-src="https://album.king-kong.org/china/MaluanHill/IMG_20250629_112927.jpg" src="https://cdn.discuss.com.hk/t/539b20/f/800x0/http://album.king-kong.org/china/MaluanHill/IMG_20250629_112927.jpg"/&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br/&gt;&lt;br/&gt;目測山體唔超過500米高, 但又有深圳最大瀑布群玩&lt;br/&gt;&lt;span class="post-img-container" data-pid="573050416" original-img="http://album.king-kong.org/china/MaluanHill/IMG_20250629_112959.jpg" style='\"display:block\"'&gt;&lt;img border="0" data-src="https://album.king-kong.org/china/MaluanHill/IMG_20250629_112959.jpg" src="https://cdn.discuss.com.hk/t/06cb05/f/800x0/http://album.king-kong.org/china/MaluanHill/IMG_20250629_112959.jpg"/&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br/&gt;&lt;br/&gt;睇來都幾多遊人來玩&lt;br/&gt;&lt;span class="post-img-container" data-pid="573050416" original-img="http://album.king-kong.org/china/MaluanHill/IMG_20250629_113419.jpg" style='\"display:block\"'&gt;&lt;img border="0" data-src="https://album.king-kong.org/china/MaluanHill/IMG_20250629_113419.jpg" src="https://cdn.discuss.com.hk/t/6e84d7/f/800x0/http://album.king-kong.org/china/MaluanHill/IMG_20250629_113419.jpg"/&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br/&gt;&lt;br/&gt;M480公車由高鐵坪山站來呢度&lt;br/&gt;&lt;span class="post-img-container" data-pid="573050416" original-img="http://album.king-kong.org/china/MaluanHill/IMG_20250629_113602.jpg" style='\"display:block\"'&gt;&lt;img border="0" data-src="https://album.king-kong.org/china/MaluanHill/IMG_20250629_113602.jpg" src="https://cdn.discuss.com.hk/t/390d1a/f/800x0/http://album.king-kong.org/china/MaluanHill/IMG_20250629_113602.jpg"/&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br/&gt;&lt;br/&gt;指示牌都好充足&lt;br/&gt;&lt;span class="post-img-container" data-pid="573050416" original-img="http://album.king-kong.org/china/MaluanHill/IMG_20250629_113639.jpg" style='\"display:block\"'&gt;&lt;img border="0" data-src="https://album.king-kong.org/china/MaluanHill/IMG_20250629_113639.jpg" src="https://cdn.discuss.com.hk/t/1c71ce/f/800x0/http://album.king-kong.org/china/MaluanHill/IMG_20250629_113639.jpg"/&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br/&gt;&lt;br/&gt;見到對岸農莊有荔枝樹過去R左幾粒食幾好味&lt;br/&gt;&lt;span class="post-img-container" data-pid="573050416" original-img="http://album.king-kong.org/china/MaluanHill/IMG_20250629_114125.jpg" style='\"display:block\"'&gt;&lt;img border="0" data-src="https://album.king-kong.org/china/MaluanHill/IMG_20250629_114125.jpg" src="https://cdn.discuss.com.hk/t/7fb59b/f/800x0/http://album.king-kong.org/china/MaluanHill/IMG_20250629_114125.jpg"/&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br/&gt;&lt;br/&gt;4蚊人仔買咗半斤一路行一路食住先&lt;br/&gt;&lt;span class="post-img-container" data-pid="573050416" original-img="http://album.king-kong.org/china/MaluanHill/IMG_20250629_114352.jpg" style='\"display:block\"'&gt;&lt;img border="0" data-src="https://album.king-kong.org/china/MaluanHill/IMG_20250629_114352.jpg" src="https://cdn.discuss.com.hk/t/4a2bee/f/800x0/http://album.king-kong.org/china/MaluanHill/IMG_20250629_114352.jpg"/&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br/&gt;&lt;br/&gt;見好多人玩緊水&lt;br/&gt;&lt;span class="post-img-container" data-pid="573050416" original-img="http://album.king-kong.org/china/MaluanHill/IMG_20250629_114205.jpg" style='\"display:block\"'&gt;&lt;img border="0" data-src="https://album.king-kong.org/china/MaluanHill/IMG_20250629_114205.jpg" src="https://cdn.discuss.com.hk/t/eea6bf/f/800x0/http://album.king-kong.org/china/MaluanHill/IMG_20250629_114205.jpg"/&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br/&gt;&lt;br/&gt;郊野公園竟然有KFC&lt;br/&gt;&lt;span class="post-img-container" data-pid="573050416" original-img="http://album.king-kong.org/china/MaluanHill/IMG_20250629_114718.jpg" style='\"display:block\"'&gt;&lt;img border="0" data-src="https://album.king-kong.org/china/MaluanHill/IMG_20250629_114718.jpg" src="https://cdn.discuss.com.hk/t/32973e/f/800x0/http://album.king-kong.org/china/MaluanHill/IMG_20250629_114718.jpg"/&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br/&gt;&lt;br/&gt;步道都係人工靚路搞得好企理&lt;br/&gt;&lt;span class="post-img-container" data-pid="573050416" original-img="http://album.king-kong.org/china/MaluanHill/IMG_20250629_115229.jpg" style='\"display:block\"'&gt;&lt;img border="0" data-src="https://album.king-kong.org/china/MaluanHill/IMG_20250629_115229.jpg" src="https://cdn.discuss.com.hk/t/762d05/f/800x0/http://album.king-kong.org/china/MaluanHill/IMG_20250629_115229.jpg"/&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br/&gt;&lt;br/&gt;咁多人影相一定有好嘢&lt;br/&gt;&lt;span class="post-img-container" data-pid="573050416" original-img="http://album.king-kong.org/china/MaluanHill/IMG_20250629_115421.jpg" style='\"display:block\"'&gt;&lt;img border="0" data-src="https://album.king-kong.org/china/MaluanHill/IMG_20250629_115421.jpg" src="https://cdn.discuss.com.hk/t/aba0ae/f/800x0/http://album.king-kong.org/china/MaluanHill/IMG_20250629_115421.jpg"/&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br/&gt;&lt;br/&gt;銀河瀑&lt;br/&gt;&lt;span class="post-img-container" data-pid="573050416" original-img="http://album.king-kong.org/china/MaluanHill/IMG_20250629_115607.jpg" style='\"display:block\"'&gt;&lt;img border="0" data-src="https://album.king-kong.org/china/MaluanHill/IMG_20250629_115607.jpg" src="https://cdn.discuss.com.hk/t/93e18c/f/800x0/http://album.king-kong.org/china/MaluanHill/IMG_20250629_115607.jpg"/&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br/&gt;&lt;br/&gt;繼續上探&lt;br/&gt;&lt;span class="post-img-container" data-pid="573050416" original-img="http://album.king-kong.org/china/MaluanHill/IMG_20250629_120130.jpg" style='\"display:block\"'&gt;&lt;img border="0" data-src="https://album.king-kong.org/china/MaluanHill/IMG_20250629_120130.jpg" src="https://cdn.discuss.com.hk/t/2a8bca/f/800x0/http://album.king-kong.org/china/MaluanHill/IMG_20250629_120130.jpg"/&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br/&gt;&lt;br/&gt;&lt;br/&gt;呢個唔知叫咩名&lt;br/&gt;&lt;span class="post-img-container" data-pid="573050416" original-img="http://album.king-kong.org/china/MaluanHill/IMG_20250629_120327.jpg" style='\"display:block\"'&gt;&lt;img border="0" data-src="https://album.king-kong.org/china/MaluanHill/IMG_20250629_120327.jpg" src="https://cdn.discuss.com.hk/t/adc8e6/f/800x0/http://album.king-kong.org/china/MaluanHill/IMG_20250629_120327.jpg"/&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br/&gt;&lt;br/&gt;&lt;br/&gt;再上探&lt;br/&gt;&lt;span class="post-img-container" data-pid="573050416" original-img="http://album.king-kong.org/china/MaluanHill/IMG_20250629_120922.jpg" style='\"display:block\"'&gt;&lt;img border="0" data-src="https://album.king-kong.org/china/MaluanHill/IMG_20250629_120922.jpg" src="https://cdn.discuss.com.hk/t/d2f390/f/800x0/http://album.king-kong.org/china/MaluanHill/IMG_20250629_120922.jpg"/&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br/&gt;&lt;br/&gt;&lt;br/&gt;跟路牌去九天瀑&lt;br/&gt;&lt;span class="post-img-container" data-pid="573050416" original-img="http://album.king-kong.org/china/MaluanHill/IMG_20250629_121209.jpg" style='\"display:block\"'&gt;&lt;img border="0" data-src="https://album.king-kong.org/china/MaluanHill/IMG_20250629_121209.jpg" src="https://cdn.discuss.com.hk/t/960a88/f/800x0/http://album.king-kong.org/china/MaluanHill/IMG_20250629_121209.jpg"/&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br/&gt;&lt;br/&gt;&lt;br/&gt;潭水比較靜位置會開放可以落去玩&lt;br/&gt;&lt;span class="post-img-container" data-pid="573050416" original-img="http://album.king-kong.org/china/MaluanHill/IMG_20250629_124151.jpg" style='\"display:block\"'&gt;&lt;img border="0" data-src="https://album.king-kong.org/china/MaluanHill/IMG_20250629_124151.jpg" src="https://cdn.discuss.com.hk/t/0697c9/f/800x0/http://album.king-kong.org/china/MaluanHill/IMG_20250629_124151.jpg"/&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br/&gt;&lt;br/&gt;&lt;br/&gt;九天瀑&lt;br/&gt;&lt;span class="post-img-container" data-pid="573050416" original-img="http://album.king-kong.org/china/MaluanHill/IMG_20250629_124806.jpg" style='\"display:block\"'&gt;&lt;img border="0" data-src="https://album.king-kong.org/china/MaluanHill/IMG_20250629_124806.jpg" src="https://cdn.discuss.com.hk/t/520c0f/f/800x0/http://album.king-kong.org/china/MaluanHill/IMG_20250629_124806.jpg"/&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br/&gt;&lt;br/&gt;&lt;br/&gt;行咗入深谷, 好處係太陽曬唔到咁多入來&lt;br/&gt;&lt;span class="post-img-container" data-pid="573050416" original-img="http://album.king-kong.org/china/MaluanHill/IMG_20250629_125409.jpg" style='\"display:block\"'&gt;&lt;img border="0" data-src="https://album.king-kong.org/china/MaluanHill/IMG_20250629_125409.jpg" src="https://cdn.discuss.com.hk/t/57ef4d/f/800x0/http://album.king-kong.org/china/MaluanHill/IMG_20250629_125409.jpg"/&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br/&gt;&lt;br/&gt;&lt;br/&gt;298米位原路折反, 門外就走出咗郊野公園範圍, 出去向前行就係東部華橋城, 大約2-3KM路程可到茶溪谷&lt;br/&gt;&lt;span class="post-img-container" data-pid="573050416" original-img="http://album.king-kong.org/china/MaluanHill/IMG_20250629_125903.jpg" style='\"display:block\"'&gt;&lt;img border="0" data-src="https://album.king-kong.org/china/MaluanHill/IMG_20250629_125903.jpg" src="https://cdn.discuss.com.hk/t/a14773/f/800x0/http://album.king-kong.org/china/MaluanHill/IMG_20250629_125903.jpg"/&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br/&gt;&lt;br/&gt;&lt;br/&gt;飛龍瀑, 呢度水急有圍封但好多人照行出去影相&lt;br/&gt;&lt;span class="post-img-container" data-pid="573050416" original-img="http://album.king-kong.org/china/MaluanHill/IMG_20250629_131020.jpg" style='\"display:block\"'&gt;&lt;img border="0" data-src="https://album.king-kong.org/china/MaluanHill/IMG_20250629_131020.jpg" src="https://cdn.discuss.com.hk/t/efde8f/f/800x0/http://album.king-kong.org/china/MaluanHill/IMG_20250629_131020.jpg"/&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br/&gt;&lt;br/&gt;&lt;br/&gt;要去打邊爐所以落山會比較趕時間&lt;br/&gt;&lt;span class="post-img-container" data-pid="573050416" original-img="http://album.king-kong.org/china/MaluanHill/IMG_20250629_131323.jpg" style='\"display:block\"'&gt;&lt;img border="0" data-src="https://album.king-kong.org/china/MaluanHill/IMG_20250629_131323.jpg" src="https://cdn.discuss.com.hk/t/a5b3c9/f/800x0/http://album.king-kong.org/china/MaluanHill/IMG_20250629_131323.jpg"/&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br/&gt;&lt;br/&gt;&lt;br/&gt;影毛蟲都玩咗成個字&lt;br/&gt;&lt;span class="post-img-container" data-pid="573050416" original-img="http://album.king-kong.org/china/MaluanHill/IMG_20250629_123305.jpg" style='\"display:block\"'&gt;&lt;img border="0" data-src="https://album.king-kong.org/china/MaluanHill/IMG_20250629_123305.jpg" src="https://cdn.discuss.com.hk/t/8bf5ef/f/800x0/http://album.king-kong.org/china/MaluanHill/IMG_20250629_123305.jpg"/&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br/&gt;&lt;br/&gt;&lt;span class="post-img-container" data-pid="573050416" original-img="http://album.king-kong.org/china/MaluanHill/IMG_20250629_132420.jpg" style='\"display:block\"'&gt;&lt;img border="0" data-src="https://album.king-kong.org/china/MaluanHill/IMG_20250629_132420.jpg" src="https://cdn.discuss.com.hk/t/d11c2a/f/800x0/http://album.king-kong.org/china/MaluanHill/IMG_20250629_132420.jpg"/&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br/&gt;&lt;br/&gt;&lt;br/&gt;水潭位可以沖下對鞋&lt;br/&gt;&lt;span class="post-img-container" data-pid="573050416" original-img="http://album.king-kong.org/china/MaluanHill/IMG_20250629_133300.jpg" style='\"display:block\"'&gt;&lt;img border="0" data-src="https://album.king-kong.org/china/MaluanHill/IMG_20250629_133300.jpg" src="https://cdn.discuss.com.hk/t/251d81/f/800x0/http://album.king-kong.org/china/MaluanHill/IMG_20250629_133300.jpg"/&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br/&gt;&lt;br/&gt;&lt;br/&gt;隊友食完話要返轉頭買荔枝&lt;br/&gt;&lt;span class="post-img-container" data-pid="573050416" original-img="http://album.king-kong.org/china/MaluanHill/IMG_20250629_140958.jpg" style='\"display:block\"'&gt;&lt;img border="0" data-src="https://album.king-kong.org/china/MaluanHill/IMG_20250629_140958.jpg" src="https://cdn.discuss.com.hk/t/38739f/f/800x0/http://album.king-kong.org/china/MaluanHill/IMG_20250629_140958.jpg"/&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br/&gt;&lt;br/&gt;&lt;br/&gt;即時剪落來賣8蚊斤抵到爛&lt;br/&gt;&lt;span class="post-img-container" data-pid="573050416" original-img="http://album.king-kong.org/china/MaluanHill/IMG_20250629_140647.jpg" style='\"display:block\"'&gt;&lt;img border="0" data-src="https://album.king-kong.org/china/MaluanHill/IMG_20250629_140647.jpg" src="https://cdn.discuss.com.hk/t/b107f3/f/800x0/http://album.king-kong.org/china/MaluanHill/IMG_20250629_140647.jpg"/&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br/&gt;&lt;br/&gt;&lt;br/&gt;睇來今年荔枝多到賣唔晒&lt;br/&gt;&lt;span class="post-img-container" data-pid="573050416" original-img="http://album.king-kong.org/china/MaluanHill/IMG_20250629_140840.jpg" style='\"display:block\"'&gt;&lt;img border="0" data-src="https://album.king-kong.org/china/MaluanHill/IMG_20250629_140840.jpg" src="https://cdn.discuss.com.hk/t/6c7d90/f/800x0/http://album.king-kong.org/china/MaluanHill/IMG_20250629_140840.jpg"/&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br/&gt;&lt;br/&gt;&lt;br/&gt;路線圖: 馬巒山郊野公園西北門 =&amp;gt; 飛龍瀑, 原路反回, 約6KM&lt;br/&gt;&lt;span class="post-img-container" data-pid="573050416" original-img="http://album.king-kong.org/china/MaluanHill/map.jpg" style='\"display:block\"'&gt;&lt;img border="0" data-src="https://album.king-kong.org/china/MaluanHill/map.jpg" src="https://cdn.discuss.com.hk/t/c6a023/f/800x0/http://album.king-kong.org/china/MaluanHill/map.jpg"/&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/br&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br/&gt;&lt;br/&gt;&lt;br/&gt; &lt;!-- google_ad_section_end --&gt;&lt;/div&gt;</content><link href="https://www.discuss.com.hk/viewthread.php?tid=31970156&amp;utm_source=festival_fid&amp;utm_medium=110&amp;utm_campaign=1076&amp;extra=page%3D1%26amp%3Bfilter%3D0%26amp%3Borderby%3Ddateline%26amp%3Bascdesc%3DDESC"/><published>2025-06-30T14:50:33+08:00</published></entry><entry><id>41f715b4679026b74505bd3a4ec8093e</id><title>2025夏 重遊長灘島</title><updated>2025-06-07T21:40:58+08:00</updated><author><name>stevenchoi</name></author><content type="html">&lt;p&gt;Published on: 2025-06-07T21:40:58+0800&lt;/p&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;div class="postmessage-content t_msgfont" id="postmessage_572739990"&gt;&lt;!-- google_ad_section_start --&gt;&lt;span id="postorig_572739990"&gt;疫情前到訪感覺熱鬧，不知為何這次感覺有點蕭條&lt;br&gt;&lt;br/&gt;&lt;span id="attach_16284476" onmouseover="showMenu(this.id, 0, 1)" style="position: absolute; display: none"&gt;&lt;img border="0" src="images/discuss_style/attachimg.gif"/&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;div class="post-img-container" data-pid="572739990" original-img="https://img.discuss.com.hk/attachments/day_250607/20250607_368e4f82d4f441163b47Ez7T1orhHVE1.jpg"&gt;&lt;img border="0" src="https://cdn.discuss.com.hk/t/249a72/f/800x0/https://img.discuss.com.hk/attachments/day_250607/20250607_368e4f82d4f441163b47Ez7T1orhHVE1.jpg"/&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div class="t_attach" id="attach_16284476_menu" style="position: absolute; display: none"&gt;&lt;img alt="" border="0" class="absmiddle" src="images/attachicons/image.gif"/&gt; &lt;a href="attachment.php?aid=16284476&amp;amp;nothumb=yes" target="_blank"&gt;&lt;strong&gt;IMG_20250529_084445.jpg&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/a&gt; (2.35 MB)&lt;br/&gt;&lt;div class="t_smallfont"&gt;2025-6-7 21:40&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;br/&gt;&lt;br/&gt;馬尼拉T3隔離的賭場吃菲律賓菜&lt;br/&gt;&lt;span id="attach_16284477" onmouseover="showMenu(this.id, 0, 1)"